ЁЯПЖBest tool made for people who want to find high traffic amazon keywords.

A brilliant members export tool that allows you to quickly export Amazon keywords to CSV with just one click!

ЁЯЦЦ  KEY FEATURES:

One-click to find high-traffic keywords and long-tail keywords.

ЁЯЪЧ DESCRIPTION Step by Step:

1.Click the search button.

тЫ╡я╕П SUPPORTED COLUMNS:

keywords
volume
target

ЁЯФО  HOW DOES IT WORK:

Using Amazon's official API to export data.
Free account can only find up to related keywords at a time.
Paid account can find related keywords and their traffic at a time. Only $9.99!

ЁЯФТ  USAGE POLICY

No password required.
All the data you export is processed locally, so no one knows what you exported.

The plugin will mention other plugins related to Amazon, so feel free to try them out if you need them.
